              "  'Advance Infradevelopers (P) Ltd. v. Adjudicating Authority, (2021) 127 taxmann.com 197 (Madras)',\n",
              "  'Smt. Parveen Amin Bhathara v. the Income Tax Officer, Writ Appeal No. 1795 of 2021 decided on 27th June 2022',\n",
              "  'Infineon Technologies AG AM Campeon v. Deputy Commissioner of Income-Tax; Writ Petition No. 49458 of 2018 decided on 24th June, 2022',\n",
